  <li>Trying to install nvidia driversâ€¦ freeze while rebooting
    <ul>
      <li>while booting enter GRUB with <code class="highlighter-rouge">Ctrl</code>+<code class="highlighter-rouge">Alt</code>+<code class="highlighter-rouge">Del</code>
        <ul>
